values: Well, i am back in Co now and on the 13th of last month i finally did it :D I had my surgery. I am now at home, healing and cant wait to be able to get back to my useual activities

Still hiding out, really miss all of my friends and family. Im not sure when ill be coming back to Colorado, or where i'll go from here. I hope you all haven't forgot about me. I guess i shoud have stayed in Alabama, I got mixed up with the rong people and things and now i regret it.

I am now settled in Colorado, i am making a lot of new friends that are very excepting and nice. I am making a lot of extra money to put back for surgery also; The snow is wonderfull, i love it but i dont drive in it, lol. I think i have finnaly found a place for myself in this world, but i do miss my kids more then anything, i hope i'll be able to go viset them soon. I have been working out all most every night since i been here, so far i have lost 9 pounds in the past 2 weeks, yay go me ! wont be long i'll be down to the recomended wieght for surgery. and i already have a new doctor too so things are looking up for me.

i got a call today, it was from my Ex. she was crying, she said my mom was being transported from one hospital to a better one. my mom has 4 blockages and need a bypass or a valve replaced, thats right , open heart surgery; my mom is a diabetic too, so its not as good as it usually is. i'm worried about her, id like to go see her but she always gets upset and mad when i do so i think its best if i just stay away, it hurts me so bad, i want to see her. ive been about to go out of my mind all day, i cant seem to do anything to keep my mind off of it.

All my life i have been left behind, rejected and used. I am so tired of it, i can't ever seem to get ahead or even get my life rolling fowards. it seems like my life would be looking up by now but no, i am still being left behind and noone seems to care as long as it doesnt get in there way. And people reather hang out with a toltal dick then someone who is a real friend. i guess most of it is my falt, maybe i should be more outgoing and pushy, but i just dont know how to be that way. i don't want pitty or for anyone to feel sorry for me; i just like to express my feeling sometimes so you'll know how worthless i am. Yeah, my life isn't the way i had thought it would be when i was younger, and it is some what depressing. I am in no position to make any changes in my life, even if i was, im not sure i'd know what to do. its strange, i useally have advice for anything and anyone but i dont have any for myself. it seems like all the changese i've made so far was pointless and worthless, i have just backed myself up into a corner and now have no way out. Yep, i have ruined my life in the worst ways posible, and i don't know how to fix it all. I do realize that every post i make is a downer, but i just don't have a life worth posting about, i never get to do anything, nope, no long walks in the park, no going swiming, no nothing, and i just get to go out maybe twice a month then im rushed to go back home. i dont have any friends, at least none that cares to talk, chat or viset with me. they're nice to me when i come around , other then that its like i'm not even in the world. im so worthless cops don't even stop me, and thats bad. anyways, ill be suprized if more then 2 people actually reads this, so please don't bother replying to any of it, its just pointless.

I knew things were going too damn good, yesterday every thing went bad real quick.i can't really explan the way i feel except the feeling of being dead on the inside, witch is a feeling i know so well. i can't wait to go back home, its all i've been ablle to think about since i got to alabama.

yep, im back in Alabama for a few days. the first few nights i slept in my truck , im spending the night with john tonight though. its weird to be back here. im going to try to make some money over the next couple days, im not sure how much i'll be able to make but i hope its enough to be worth it. every thing has been going ok so far, cept my oldest brother, he fussed at me for 2 hours today about the way i am , he ever read from the bible for a while. my mom has been giveing me some mean looks but she hasn't said anything, yet. i watched that new movie, the hill's have eyes, it is really messed up, too much gore for me, and it didnt end right, plus some things in it botherd me some. i should be heading back to Nashville monday, i can't wait. i really miss Nashville and my Girlfriend. anyway's, i'll see you kids latters.

hopefully i will be adding more states over the next few years, i love to traval and see new places
create your own visited states map or check out these Google Hacks.
yep, my new boyfriend dumped me, his family was teaseing him about dateing someone like me and he couldn't take it so he dumped me. eh o well, i'll live, i always do

john has me to go get some food from Hardees last night, well the guy that was working the window started talking to me,  he gave me his phone number and asked me if i wanted to go out,  so as of now i am going to see him tonight at work, spend the day with him tomarrow and  he said he is going to take me out on a date when he gets paid wensday   , YAY  , i have a boyfriend :)
have i ever said how much i like the little kitty mood emotion thingy's ?

I would like to update you all tonight but.... i have had a lil too much brandy and need to be laying down right now so i'll try to udate tomarrow night , and yeah its good :) at least i think it is.  YAY go me  :D
My room mate informed my EX today that he's knows i have a lot of money in a bank acc , and if i dont start paying all the bills , he is going to through me out come monday

I went to look at the apartment today and see about it,,, its going to be a lot more then what they said over the phone and on top of that , with all of the deposits it will take around 600 to get in it :( i don't think i can pull it off, even if i do , it will only leave me with about 60 bucks to live off of per month , no more laser hair treatments or anything. looks like im out of luck, i dont know how i could come up with 600 to start off with, i guess i'm going to have a heart to heart with my rommy tonight, either two things can happen, 1 he will beat the @#$%^ out of me and make me give him all of my money anyways or 2 he will through me out and still end up beaten

I'm probably going to have to rent one of those storage thingys and put all of my stuff in it and take off for a while, things went south quick. i am looking for a cheap place to rent , i dont care if its a dump , but i have had no luck so far. my roomy is not only at the verge of being abusive but i think he has been stealing some of my money i had hid in my truck , he comes in my room when im asleep and probably got the key to my truck to get in it. he spys on me and trys to read what im typing to my friends on yahoo. I really need to find a way out, sometimes i feel like id be better off to just give him all of my money, and then take a hot bath with a razor blade. i know i cant take much more, im so stressed out right now, my hands are shakeing. i cant seem to think any more, or even care. some times i just wish he would go ahead and beat the crap out of me and get it over with. i actualy keep myself locked in my bedroom all the time.

ok for those of you who doesn't know yet,.....  i am now divorced. i am staying with my ex's brother and he is an ass most of the time,  theres a few times that he came in my room screaming at me, yelling and i thought he was going to hit me, all i could do was  sit here and cry. i am looking for a new place to live but can't offord much.  other then that , i'm doing pretty good, i have a new truck so i can get around, i've started laser hair removal and i am  looking foward to the years to come.  I lost my doctor due to a change in insurance so now i have to find a new one.    anyways , i'll post more for  y'all latter.

 

*huggle's*
